_sText:
Welcome to Fy_Iceworld_Redefined!!

Credits: To whoever came up with the original idea of Iceworld/Mr. Stealth, because I used his version of iceworld to help me make my own.

I made this map a while back, and originally did release it, but for some reason I trashed it after a week.  I've decided to re-release it, for an unknown reason.

Changes:
-Texture changes, which I think give the map a new feel.
-Optimization changes
-Raised guns
-Stairs to platform in the center, to hopefully make the game-play a little more exciting
-New lighting


If you like Iceworld, this is the map for you.  I hope you all enjoy, and as always, comments and ratings are greatly appreciated!
